10251370@unknown@formal@none@1@S@{{IPA|/ˈki.el vi no.ˈmi.ʤas/}}@1@3@@oe@30-11-2008
10251380@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* My name is...: ''Mi nomiĝas...''@1@6@@oe@30-11-2008
10251390@unknown@formal@none@1@S@{{IPA|/mi no.ˈmi.ʤas/}}@1@2@@oe@30-11-2008
10251400@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* How much (is it/are they)?: ''Kiom (estas)?''@1@8@@oe@30-11-2008
10251410@unknown@formal@none@1@S@{{IPA|/ˈki.om ˈes.tas/}}@1@2@@oe@30-11-2008
10251420@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* Here you are: ''Jen'' {{IPA|/jen/}}@1@6@@oe@30-11-2008
10251430@unknown@formal@none@1@S@* Do you speak Esperanto?: ''Ĉu vi parolas Esperanton?''@1@9@@oe@30-11-2008
